channel.title: RuneWings317
channel.description:
Hey guys!
I am moving from Delta to Project Insanity. Last source I had, I was the only one who scripted, so I need some people (3) who can script! The application and the spaces open are listed below.
Spaces: [s]1. Client ~ Must be able to add models (items, objects, NPCs), make a Project Insanity Webclient* and maybe add some animations/GFXs.[/s] 2. Site Scripter ~ Must be able to code in HTML, MySQL and PHP. 3. Server Scripter ~ Must be amazing at it.
Please, only put in an application if your good at coding!
Application: [code]RuneWings317 Application In Game Name: Age(14+): Country (for time reason): How long have you been around RSPS: How long have you been coding: How much will you be on the server a day: Do you have skype: Will you be active (forums and in game): Other Info:
I Agree that I am of the age I stated and that I will not violate any in game rules or forum rules (yes/no):[/code]
Other Info: 1. Reward ~ You will be awarded with Owner Status. You must do something in your space before you get the Owner status. 2. I will get back to you within 24 hours with a PM.
If you have any other questions please post!
XLdarkwingLX
*Webclient is already half made. Need help finishing it.
